detail.name: Super Baby 2
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 4 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 card with 《Brainwashed》 or 《Machine Mutant》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of their owner's deck in a random order.
